# ansible-galaxy

> Create and manage Ansible roles
> More information: https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/cli/ansible-galaxy.html

- Install a role:

`ansible-galaxy install {string user}.{any something}`

- Remove a role:

`ansible-galaxy remove {string user}.{any something}`

- List installed roles:

`ansible-galaxy list`

- Search for a given role:

`ansible-galaxy search {any something}`

- Create a new role:

`ansible-galaxy init {any something}`

- Get information about a user role:

`ansible-galaxy role info {string user}.{any something}`

- Get information about a collection:

`ansible-galaxy collection info {string user}.{any something}`
